    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >……在预知未来变化的情况下，你需要多少个 <strong><i>orrb</i></strong> 才能成功？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >了解机制如何运作。预测它们将如何相互作用。验证你的推测。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822180/extras/a0e873bae7c7159bee1435a41f3e8d39.poster.avif?t=1772266611\" width=1170 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822180/extras/a0e873bae7c7159bee1435a41f3e8d39.webm?t=1772266611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822180/extras/a0e873bae7c7159bee1435a41f3e8d39.mp4?t=1772266611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索关卡。放置图块。构建路径。释放 <strong><i>orrb</i></strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822180/extras/ba0b500380ac93b7e2407e84938f80ae.poster.avif?t=1772266611\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822180/extras/ba0b500380ac93b7e2407e84938f80ae.webm?t=1772266611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822180/extras/ba0b500380ac93b7e2407e84938f80ae.mp4?t=1772266611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>256+ 个关卡</strong>，精心设计并手工打造，循序渐进地引入机制、讲解规则，并逐步提升挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>20+ 种图块类型</strong>，用于搭建 <strong><i>orrb</i></strong> 的行进路径</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3+ 个区域</strong>，每个区域都有其独特的挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无时间限制</strong>——在发射 <strong><i>orrb</i></strong> 之前，尽情布置、检查、再检查……甚至检查第三遍</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>简洁的界面与直观的交互</strong>，完全支持仅用鼠标操作（同时支持其他输入方式）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822180/extras/bf7bbf03205e23ad52bad5c6c39812ec.poster.avif?t=1772266611\" width=1170 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822180/extras/bf7bbf03205e23ad52bad5c6c39812ec.webm?t=1772266611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822180/extras/bf7bbf03205e23ad52bad5c6c39812ec.mp4?t=1772266611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>orrb</i></strong> 是由我独立开发的个人独立游戏项目（你好！）。作为一名独立开发者，我的目标是在这一媒介中探索各种创意，并希望在未来持续创作小而精致的高质量作品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任何建设性的反馈都非常欢迎。请随时与我联系——我会尽力快速回复消息，并及时修复可能出现的问题。</p>",
